commit.message: Added transcript to search API result

Added GCS blob caching
* Removes the need to process input files if they are already in the GCS
bucket
Refactored backend route and fixed issue with input file hashing

Optimized searching
* Introduced result caching so that transcriptions and matches can be
reused
Fixed search result response on API
Modified results page list item group style to fit with bottom border
Added base64 decoding of file input
Working interface between server and client
